Examples
========

Command line
------------

.. image:: docs/images/example.png
   :width: 60%

.. code-block:: text

   $ terminal_graphics show examples/lenna.png
   $ terminal_graphics info

.. code-block:: text

   $ terminal_graphics show $(fzf)

Scripting
---------

.. code-block:: python

   from terminal_graphics import write_file

   write_file('examples/lenna.png')


